{"type":"user","uuid":"ce5cb228-36b7-48ea-8391-0ef3a7a13de5","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde972bc4470cb1b5cb5995e775f9","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Command: wc -l /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/006-safety-and-permission-guard/spec.md && echo \"---\" && head -20 /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/006-safety-and-permission-guard/spec.md\nStdout:      115 /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/006-safety-and-permission-guard/spec.md\n---\n# F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n\n## Summary\n\n为 Telegram 管道控制增加安全护栏：用户权限分级、高风险命令授权校验、参数净化、敏感操作二次确认与审计日志。重点覆盖 stop/reset/retry/exec 等高风险指令，确保\"可用\"与\"可控\"并存。\n\n**Scope**: 权限分级模型、高风险命令拦截、参数净化、确认机制、审计日志。\n\n**Dependencies**: F-002 (Telegram Pipeline Command Router - completed), F-004 (Pipeline Process Controller - completed)\n\n---\n\n## User Stories\n\n### US-1: User Permission Levels\n\n**As a** 系统管理员 **I want** 基于用户 ID 的权限分级机制 **So that** 不同用户拥有不同的操作权限\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-1.1: 支持三级权限: `admin` | `operator` | `viewer`\n\nStderr: (empty)\nExit Code: 0\nSignal: (none)"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_e6eee94544c64ef2895c25f4","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:29:36.815Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"8785aa39-db93-42cc-9135-6d55080bf146","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_e6eee94544c64ef2895c25f4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three planning artifacts have been successfully created:\n\n---\n\n## Planning Complete for F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n\n| File | Lines | Description |\n|------|-------|-------------|\n| `spec.md` | 115 | Feature specification with 5 user stories, NFRs, scope boundaries, and decisions |\n| `plan.md` | ~400 | Architecture, 5 components, 5 interface APIs, 4 data models, testing strategy |\n| `tasks.md` | ~160 | 22 tasks across 4 phases (Setup → Foundational → User Stories → Polish) |\n\n### Key Design Decisions:\n\n1. **Permission Model**: Three-level hierarchy (admin/operator/viewer) with `USER_PERMISSIONS` env config\n2. **Confirmation Flow**: Text-based \"CONFIRM\" response (not inline keyboard), 60s timeout, `--force` flag for admin\n3. **Audit Logging**: JSON Lines format in `logs/audit.log` with rotation (10MB/5 files)\n4. **Parameter Sanitization**: Path traversal and shell metacharacter rejection\n\n### Critical Path:\n```\nT-001 (config) → T-010 (permission) → T-012 (middleware) → T-110 (router integration) → T-130 (stop confirmation) → T-904 (integration tests)\n```\n\n### Parallelizable Tasks:\n- T-010, T-011, T-013 (foundational security modules)\n- T-900, T-901, T-902 (unit tests)\n\n---\n\n**COMPLETION_SIGNAL**: F-006 planning complete. Ready for task assignment to Dev Agent.\n\n[Agent ID: agent-d7b8bb9c]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_e6eee94544c64ef2895c25f4","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:29:45.509Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
