{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312043152b5036384e84b43d1","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"id":"20260312043152b5036384e84b43d1","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde9957907adcaf7ecdb9c669f2d5","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.env.example"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":21197,"output_tokens":258,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_ccbecff65fa64c6b898f8181","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:31:57.726Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"ecb1a499-6e31-4f49-bbbf-a4123e28c0ac","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde99530404a4b45df1f18647766a","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→为 Telegram 管道控制增加安全护栏：用户权限分级、高风险命令授权校验、参数净化、敏感操作二次确认与审计日志。重点覆盖 stop/reset/retry/exec 等高风险指令，确保\"可用\"与\"可控\"并存。\n   6→\n   7→**Scope**: 权限分级模型、高风险命令拦截、参数净化、确认机制、审计日志。\n   8→\n   9→**Dependencies**: F-002 (Telegram Pipeline Command Router - completed), F-004 (Pipeline Process Controller - completed)\n  10→\n  11→---\n  12→\n  13→## User Stories\n  14→\n  15→### US-1: User Permission Levels\n  16→\n  17→**As a** 系统管理员 **I want** 基于用户 ID 的权限分级机制 **So that** 不同用户拥有不同的操作权限\n  18→\n  19→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  20→- AC-1.1: 支持三级权限: `admin` | `operator` | `viewer`\n  21→- AC-1.2: 通过环境变量 `USER_PERMISSIONS` 配置用户权限映射\n  22→- AC-1.3: 未配置时所有授权用户默认为 `operator`\n  23→- AC-1.4: 提供 `getUserPermission(userId)` API 查询用户权限级别\n  24→\n  25→### US-2: High-Risk Command Authorization\n  26→\n  27→**As a** 系统管理员 **I want** 高风险命令需要特定权限级别才能执行 **So that** 敏感操作不会被未授权用户触发\n  28→\n  29→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  30→- AC-2.1: 定义高风险命令列表: `stop`, `reset`, `retry`, `exec`, `force-unlock`\n  31→- AC-2.2: `stop`/`reset`/`force-unlock` 需要 `admin` 权限\n  32→- AC-2.3: `retry` 需要 `operator` 权限\n  33→- AC-2.4: `exec` 需要 `admin` 权限且受 `ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC` 控制\n  34→- AC-2.5: 权限不足时返回统一拒绝消息，不暴露敏感信息\n  35→\n  36→### US-3: Parameter Sanitization\n  37→\n  38→**As a** 系统 **I want** 所有命令参数经过净化与规则校验 **So that** 非法路径与危险参数组合被拒绝\n  39→\n  40→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  41→- AC-3.1: 路径参数禁止 `..`、绝对路径穿越、shell 元字符\n  42→- AC-3.2: targetId 参数仅允许 `[A-Za-z0-9_-]+` 格式\n  43→- AC-3.3: 拒绝包含 `; | & $ \\` ' \" ( ) < >` 等危险字符的参数\n  44→- AC-3.4: 提供 `sanitizePath()` 和 `sanitizeTargetId()` 工具函数\n  45→\n  46→### US-4: Confirmation for Sensitive Actions\n  47→\n  48→**As a** 用户 **I want** 高风险命令执行前需要明确确认 **So that** 误操作可以被及时阻止\n  49→\n  50→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  51→- AC-4.1: `stop`、`reset`、`force-unlock` 需要二次确认\n  52→- AC-4.2: 确认消息包含操作摘要和风险提示\n  53→- AC-4.3: 用户需在 60 秒内回复确认，否则操作取消\n  54→- AC-4.4: 支持 `--force` 标志跳过确认（仅限 `admin` 用户）\n  55→\n  56→### US-5: Audit Logging\n  57→\n  58→**As a** 运维人员 **I want** 每次敏感操作都写入审计日志 **So that** 我可以追溯操作历史\n  59→\n  60→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  61→- AC-5.1: 审计日志记录: timestamp, userId, username, action, params, result\n  62→- AC-5.2: 日志存储于 `logs/audit.log`（JSON Lines 格式）\n  63→- AC-5.3: 提供按会话 ID 或用户 ID 检索审计记录的 API\n  64→- AC-5.4: 日志轮转: 单文件最大 10MB，保留最近 5 个文件\n  65→\n  66→---\n  67→\n  68→## Non-Functional Requirements\n  69→\n  70→- **NFR-1 Performance**: 权限检查 < 5ms，参数净化 < 2ms，审计日志异步写入\n  71→- **NFR-2 Reliability**: 审计日志写入失败不影响命令执行，确认超时无死锁\n  72→- **NFR-3 Maintainability**: 权限配置与代码分离，高风险命令列表可配置，测试覆盖率 > 90%\n  73→- **NFR-4 Security**: 不在错误消息中暴露内部路径或配置，审计日志不可被普通用户访问\n  74→\n  75→---\n  76→\n  77→## Scope Boundaries\n  78→\n  79→**In Scope**: 用户权限分级模型与配置、高风险命令授权检查中间件、参数净化工具函数、确认对话机制、审计日志服务\n  80→\n  81→**Out of Scope**: 用户认证（已有 `isAllowedUser`）、Web UI 权限管理、数据库存储、加密存储\n  82→\n  83→---\n  84→\n  85→## High-Risk Command Matrix\n  86→\n  87→| Command | Min Permission | Confirmation | Notes |\n  88→|---------|---------------|--------------|-------|\n  89→| `stop` | admin | Yes (--force skips) | 停止运行中管道 |\n  90→| `reset` | admin | Yes (--force skips) | 重置管道状态 |\n  91→| `retry` | operator | No | 重试失败目标 |\n  92→| `exec` | admin | No | 执行系统命令 |\n  93→| `force-unlock` | admin | Yes (--force skips) | 强制释放锁 |\n  94→\n  95→---\n  96→\n  97→## Configuration\n  98→\n  99→```env\n 100→USER_PERMISSIONS=123456789:admin,987654321:operator\n 101→AUDIT_LOG_DIR=logs\n 102→AUDIT_LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB=10\n 103→AUDIT_LOG_MAX_FILES=5\n 104→```\n 105→\n 106→---\n 107→\n 108→## Decisions\n 109→\n 110→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 111→|----|------|----------|\n 112→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | 使用三级权限模型（admin/operator/viewer）|\n 113→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 确认机制使用文字确认（\"CONFIRM\"），不依赖 inline keyboard |\n 114→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 审计日志使用 JSON Lines 格式 |\n 115→| D4 | 2026-03-12 | `--force` 标志仅限 admin 用户 |\n 116→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_ccbecff65fa64c6b898f8181","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:31:57.728Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"2ef852a6-9509-4545-8e51-6c6c31cd57cc","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde9954d549ae701814caaf585949","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→DOC_LEVEL: L1\n   2→MODULE: runtime\n   3→PATH: src/**\n   4→DESCRIPTION: telegram + web request handling + sessioned CodeBuddy bridge\n   5→\n   6→ENTRYPOINT:\n   7→- src/index.js -> createHttpServer + optional Telegram bot launch\n   8→\n   9→KEY_FILES:\n  10→- src/config.js\n  11→- src/http/server.js\n  12→- src/routes/api-routes.js\n  13→- src/services/chat-service.js\n  14→- src/services/pipeline-control-service.js\n  15→- src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js\n  16→- src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js\n  17→- src/pipeline-infra/script-runner.js\n  18→- src/adapters/codebuddy.js\n  19→- src/bot/telegram.js\n  20→- src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js\n  21→- src/services/system-exec-service.js\n  22→\n  23→SUBDIRS:\n  24→- src/adapters -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/adapters.prizm\n  25→- src/bot -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm\n  26→- src/http -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/http.prizm\n  27→- src/routes -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/routes.prizm\n  28→- src/security -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/security.prizm\n  29→- src/services -> .prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm\n  30→- src/pipeline-infra -> .prizm-docs/runtime/pipeline-infra.prizm\n  31→- src/utils -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/utils.prizm\n  32→\n  33→INTERFACES:\n  34→- HTTP: /healthz, /api/events(SSE), /api/chat, /api/chat/reset, /api/screenshot, /api/system/exec\n  35→- Telegram: /start, /help, /reset, /screenshot, /exec, /pipeline, /bugfix, /planner, /status, /logs, /stop, /plan, text message relay\n  36→\n  37→TRAPS:\n  38→- ENABLE_TELEGRAM=true requires TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\n  39→- system exec is disabled unless ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC=true\n  40→- system exec requires ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES whitelist\n  41→- chat is serialized per session via chat-queue\n  42→\n  43→DECISIONS:\n  44→- 2026-03-09 | runtime-doc-init | model first-pass runtime map from source + API surface\n  45→- 2026-03-10 | runtime-infra-f001 | expose pipeline infra config in src/config.js and pipeline-control-service API for feature/bugfix run/status/stop/retry/logs/reset\n  46→- 2026-03-12 | runtime-f002 | add command routing layer for pipeline commands (/pipeline, /bugfix, /planner, /status, /logs, /stop)\n  47→- 2026-03-12 | runtime-f003 | add plan ingestion service for feature-list/bug-fix-list upload, validation, version management, and /plan command\n  48→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_ccbecff65fa64c6b898f8181","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:31:57.728Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"7a1dfd3f-0d2e-49b4-816b-429aa2ef5f33","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde99566105277b4a8f83c339818b","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→import 'dotenv/config';\n   2→import { z } from 'zod';\n   3→\n   4→import { loadPipelineInfraConfig } from './pipeline-infra/config-loader.js';\n   5→import { resolveDaemonLogPaths } from './pipeline-infra/path-policy.js';\n   6→\n   7→const schema = z.object({\n   8→  TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN: z.string().optional().default(''),\n   9→  ENABLE_TELEGRAM: z.string().optional().default('true'),\n  10→  ALLOWED_USER_IDS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n  11→  CODEBUDDY_BIN: z.string().min(1).default('codebuddy'),\n  12→  CODEBUDDY_PERMISSION_FLAG: z.string().default('-y'),\n  13→  CODEBUDDY_ECHO_STDIO: z.string().optional().default('true'),\n  14→  CODEBUDDY_HEARTBEAT_MS: z.coerce.number().int().nonnegative().default(15000),\n  15→  TELEGRAM_FILE_ALLOWED_ROOTS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n  16→  TELEGRAM_FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n  17→  REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS: z.coerce.number().int().nonnegative().default(120000),\n  18→  MAX_PROMPT_CHARS: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(8000),\n  19→  MAX_HISTORY_TURNS: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(10),\n  20→  WEB_HOST: z.string().default('127.0.0.1'),\n  21→  WEB_PORT: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(8787),\n  22→  ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC: z.string().optional().default('false'),\n  23→  ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES: z.string().optional().default(''),\n  24→  SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(60000),\n  25→  LOG_LEVEL: z.enum(['fatal', 'error', 'warn', 'info', 'debug', 'trace', 'silent']).default('info')\n  26→});\n  27→\n  28→const parsed = schema.parse(process.env);\n  29→\n  30→function parseAllowedUserIds(input) {\n  31→  return new Set(\n  32→    input\n  33→      .split(',')\n  34→      .map((id) => id.trim())\n  35→      .filter(Boolean)\n  36→  );\n  37→}\n  38→\n  39→function parseCsvList(input) {\n  40→  return input\n  41→    .split(',')\n  42→    .map((item) => item.trim())\n  43→    .filter(Boolean);\n  44→}\n  45→\n  46→function parseBoolean(input) {\n  47→  const normalized = (input ?? '').trim().toLowerCase();\n  48→  return normalized === '1' || normalized === 'true' || normalized === 'yes' || normalized === 'on';\n  49→}\n  50→\n  51→const enableTelegram = parseBoolean(parsed.ENABLE_TELEGRAM);\n  52→if (enableTelegram && !parsed.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN) {\n  53→  throw new Error('ENABLE_TELEGRAM=true 时必须提供 TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN');\n  54→}\n  55→\n  56→const pipelineInfra = loadPipelineInfraConfig({\n  57→  env: process.env,\n  58→  argv: process.argv.slice(2),\n  59→  cwd: process.cwd()\n  60→});\n  61→\n  62→const daemonLogPaths = resolveDaemonLogPaths(pipelineInfra.projectRoot);\n  63→\n  64→export const config = Object.freeze({\n  65→  telegramBotToken: parsed.TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN,\n  66→  enableTelegram,\n  67→  allowedUserIds: parseAllowedUserIds(parsed.ALLOWED_USER_IDS),\n  68→  codebuddyBin: parsed.CODEBUDDY_BIN,\n  69→  codebuddyPermissionFlag: parsed.CODEBUDDY_PERMISSION_FLAG,\n  70→  codebuddyEchoStdio: parseBoolean(parsed.CODEBUDDY_ECHO_STDIO),\n  71→  codebuddyHeartbeatMs: parsed.CODEBUDDY_HEARTBEAT_MS,\n  72→  telegramFileAllowedRoots: parseCsvList(parsed.TELEGRAM_FILE_ALLOWED_ROOTS),\n  73→  telegramFileCandidateDirs: parseCsvList(parsed.TELEGRAM_FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS),\n  74→  requestTimeoutMs: parsed.REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS,\n  75→  maxPromptChars: parsed.MAX_PROMPT_CHARS,\n  76→  maxHistoryTurns: parsed.MAX_HISTORY_TURNS,\n  77→  webHost: parsed.WEB_HOST,\n  78→  webPort: parsed.WEB_PORT,\n  79→  enableSystemExec: parseBoolean(parsed.ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC),\n  80→  allowedCommandPrefixes: parseCsvList(parsed.ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES),\n  81→  systemExecTimeoutMs: parsed.SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS,\n  82→  logLevel: parsed.LOG_LEVEL,\n  83→  pipelineInfra: Object.freeze({\n  84→    ...pipelineInfra,\n  85→    daemonLogPaths\n  86→  })\n  87→});\n  88→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_ccbecff65fa64c6b898f8181","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:31:57.728Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"fbc6e4f8-7ac8-439d-a3ff-75a3451942f7","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde9957907adcaf7ecdb9c669f2d5","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# Channel switches\n   2→ENABLE_TELEGRAM=true\n   3→\n   4→# Telegram\n   5→# 填你的 Bot Token。不要把真实 token 提交到仓库。\n   6→TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=\n   7→# ALLOWED_USER_IDS 留空 = 不限制用户ID（任何能访问你 Bot 的用户都可用）\n   8→# 建议生产环境填写，例如: ALLOWED_USER_IDS=12345678,99887766\n   9→ALLOWED_USER_IDS=\n  10→\n  11→# CodeBuddy CLI\n  12→CODEBUDDY_BIN=codebuddy\n  13→CODEBUDDY_PERMISSION_FLAG=-y\n  14→CODEBUDDY_ECHO_STDIO=true\n  15→CODEBUDDY_HEARTBEAT_MS=15000\n  16→# 可选：覆盖文件发送安全根目录（逗号分隔绝对路径）。留空则用默认值。\n  17→TELEGRAM_FILE_ALLOWED_ROOTS=\n  18→# 可选：覆盖文件候选搜索目录（逗号分隔绝对路径）。留空则用默认值。\n  19→TELEGRAM_FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS=\n  20→REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS=120000\n  21→MAX_PROMPT_CHARS=8000\n  22→MAX_HISTORY_TURNS=10\n  23→\n  24→# Web management panel\n  25→WEB_HOST=127.0.0.1\n  26→WEB_PORT=8787\n  27→\n  28→# System operation permissions (DANGEROUS, use whitelist)\n  29→ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC=false\n  30→ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES=ls,pwd,open,codebuddy,node,npm,python3\n  31→SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS=60000\n  32→\n  33→# Pipeline infra\n  34→PIPELINE_PROJECT_ROOT=\n  35→PIPELINE_DIR=\n  36→FEATURE_LIST_PATH=feature-list.json\n  37→BUG_FIX_LIST_PATH=bug-fix-list.json\n  38→MAX_RETRIES=3\n  39→SESSION_TIMEOUT=0\n  40→HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL=30\n  41→AI_CLI=cbc\n  42→PRIZMKIT_PLATFORM=codebuddy\n  43→\n  44→# Logging\n  45→LOG_LEVEL=info\n  46→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_ccbecff65fa64c6b898f8181","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:31:57.729Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
