security module details\n 181→  - Input: Security implementation\n 182→  - Output: L2 Prizm doc with KEY_FILES, INTERFACES, TRAPS\n 183→  - Acceptance: All security files documented\n 184→  - Complexity: Low\n 185→\n 186→---\n 187→\n 188→## Dependency Graph\n 189→\n 190→```\n 191→T-001 ──┬── T-010 ── T-011 ── T-101\n 192→        │\n 193→        └── T-012 ── T-013 ── T-103\n 194→\n 195→T-002 ──── T-016 ── T-017 ── T-107\n 196→                      │\n 197→                      └── T-108\n 198→\n 199→T-003 (parallel)\n 200→\n 201→T-014 ── T-015 ── T-104 ── T-105 ── T-106\n 202→\n 203→T-901 depends on: T-101, T-103, T-106, T-107\n 204→T-902, T-903 (parallel, can start after core modules complete)\n 205→```\n 206→\n 207→---\n 208→\n 209→## Parallel Execution Groups\n 210→\n 211→| Group | Tasks | Can Run In Parallel |\n 212→|-------|-------|---------------------|\n 213→| G1 | T-001, T-002, T-003 | ✓ (all setup tasks) |\n 214→| G2 | T-010, T-012 | ✓ (independent modules) |\n 215→| G3 | T-102, T-107 | ✓ (metadata additions) |\n 216→| G4 | T-902, T-903 | ✓ (documentation) |\n 217→\n 218→---\n 219→\n 220→## Summary\n 221→\n 222→| Phase | Task Count | Estimated Complexity |\n 223→|-------|------------|---------------------|\n 224→| Setup | 3 | Low |\n 225→| Foundational | 8 | Medium |\n 226→| User Stories | 8 | Medium-High |\n 227→| Polish | 3 | Low-Medium |\n 228→| **Total** | **22** | |\n 229→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_ccbecff65fa64c6b898f8181","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:38:04.340Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
