{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031204533262bae4bc2fd54d14","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"id":"2026031204533262bae4bc2fd54d14","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_c16a579ec2594523a443402f","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.codebuddy/skills/prizmkit-summarize/assets/registry-template.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":46649,"output_tokens":183,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:53:38.338Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"908375cf-46b4-424c-afc3-e9abeb4bcd42","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_0e16055c07ab494b87b27d8b","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→为 Telegram 管道控制增加安全护栏：用户权限分级、高风险命令授权校验、参数净化、敏感操作二次确认与审计日志。重点覆盖 stop/reset/retry/exec 等高风险指令，确保\"可用\"与\"可控\"并存。\n   6→\n   7→**Scope**: 权限分级模型、高风险命令拦截、参数净化、确认机制、审计日志。\n   8→\n   9→**Dependencies**: F-002 (Telegram Pipeline Command Router - completed), F-004 (Pipeline Process Controller - completed)\n  10→\n  11→---\n  12→\n  13→## User Stories\n  14→\n  15→### US-1: User Permission Levels\n  16→\n  17→**As a** 系统管理员 **I want** 基于用户 ID 的权限分级机制 **So that** 不同用户拥有不同的操作权限\n  18→\n  19→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  20→- AC-1.1: 支持三级权限: `admin` | `operator` | `viewer`\n  21→- AC-1.2: 通过环境变量 `USER_PERMISSIONS` 配置用户权限映射\n  22→- AC-1.3: 未配置时所有授权用户默认为 `operator`\n  23→- AC-1.4: 提供 `getUserPermission(userId)` API 查询用户权限级别\n  24→\n  25→### US-2: High-Risk Command Authorization\n  26→\n  27→**As a** 系统管理员 **I want** 高风险命令需要特定权限级别才能执行 **So that** 敏感操作不会被未授权用户触发\n  28→\n  29→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  30→- AC-2.1: 定义高风险命令列表: `stop`, `reset`, `retry`, `exec`, `force-unlock`\n  31→- AC-2.2: `stop`/`reset`/`force-unlock` 需要 `admin` 权限\n  32→- AC-2.3: `retry` 需要 `operator` 权限\n  33→- AC-2.4: `exec` 需要 `admin` 权限且受 `ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC` 控制\n  34→- AC-2.5: 权限不足时返回统一拒绝消息，不暴露敏感信息\n  35→\n  36→### US-3: Parameter Sanitization\n  37→\n  38→**As a** 系统 **I want** 所有命令参数经过净化与规则校验 **So that** 非法路径与危险参数组合被拒绝\n  39→\n  40→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  41→- AC-3.1: 路径参数禁止 `..`、绝对路径穿越、shell 元字符\n  42→- AC-3.2: targetId 参数仅允许 `[A-Za-z0-9_-]+` 格式\n  43→- AC-3.3: 拒绝包含 `; | & $ \\` ' \" ( ) < >` 等危险字符的参数\n  44→- AC-3.4: 提供 `sanitizePath()` 和 `sanitizeTargetId()` 工具函数\n  45→\n  46→### US-4: Confirmation for Sensitive Actions\n  47→\n  48→**As a** 用户 **I want** 高风险命令执行前需要明确确认 **So that** 误操作可以被及时阻止\n  49→\n  50→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  51→- AC-4.1: `stop`、`reset`、`force-unlock` 需要二次确认\n  52→- AC-4.2: 确认消息包含操作摘要和风险提示\n  53→- AC-4.3: 用户需在 60 秒内回复确认，否则操作取消\n  54→- AC-4.4: 支持 `--force` 标志跳过确认（仅限 `admin` 用户）\n  55→\n  56→### US-5: Audit Logging\n  57→\n  58→**As a** 运维人员 **I want** 每次敏感操作都写入审计日志 **So that** 我可以追溯操作历史\n  59→\n  60→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  61→- AC-5.1: 审计日志记录: timestamp, userId, username, action, params, result\n  62→- AC-5.2: 日志存储于 `logs/audit.log`（JSON Lines 格式）\n  63→- AC-5.3: 提供按会话 ID 或用户 ID 检索审计记录的 API\n  64→- AC-5.4: 日志轮转: 单文件最大 10MB，保留最近 5 个文件\n  65→\n  66→---\n  67→\n  68→## Non-Functional Requirements\n  69→\n  70→- **NFR-1 Performance**: 权限检查 < 5ms，参数净化 < 2ms，审计日志异步写入\n  71→- **NFR-2 Reliability**: 审计日志写入失败不影响命令执行，确认超时无死锁\n  72→- **NFR-3 Maintainability**: 权限配置与代码分离，高风险命令列表可配置，测试覆盖率 > 90%\n  73→- **NFR-4 Security**: 不在错误消息中暴露内部路径或配置，审计日志不可被普通用户访问\n  74→\n  75→---\n  76→\n  77→## Scope Boundaries\n  78→\n  79→**In Scope**: 用户权限分级模型与配置、高风险命令授权检查中间件、参数净化工具函数、确认对话机制、审计日志服务\n  80→\n  81→**Out of Scope**: 用户认证（已有 `isAllowedUser`）、Web UI 权限管理、数据库存储、加密存储\n  82→\n  83→---\n  84→\n  85→## High-Risk Command Matrix\n  86→\n  87→| Command | Min Permission | Confirmation | Notes |\n  88→|---------|---------------|--------------|-------|\n  89→| `stop` | admin | Yes (--force skips) | 停止运行中管道 |\n  90→| `reset` | admin | Yes (--force skips) | 重置管道状态 |\n  91→| `retry` | operator | No | 重试失败目标 |\n  92→| `exec` | admin | No | 执行系统命令 |\n  93→| `force-unlock` | admin | Yes (--force skips) | 强制释放锁 |\n  94→\n  95→---\n  96→\n  97→## Configuration\n  98→\n  99→```env\n 100→USER_PERMISSIONS=123456789:admin,987654321:operator\n 101→AUDIT_LOG_DIR=logs\n 102→AUDIT_LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB=10\n 103→AUDIT_LOG_MAX_FILES=5\n 104→```\n 105→\n 106→---\n 107→\n 108→## Decisions\n 109→\n 110→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 111→|----|------|----------|\n 112→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | 使用三级权限模型（admin/operator/viewer）|\n 113→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 确认机制使用文字确认（\"CONFIRM\"），不依赖 inline keyboard |\n 114→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 审计日志使用 JSON Lines 格式 |\n 115→| D4 | 2026-03-12 | `--force` 标志仅限 admin 用户 |\n 116→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_0e16055c07ab494b87b27d8b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:53:38.340Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"368681a0-e033-49df-a78b-75152b8b15c5","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_eae735c497af42f4877ad667","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# Feature Registry\n   2→\n   3→| ID | Slug | Title | Status | Last Updated |\n   4→|----|------|-------|--------|--------------|\n   5→| F-001 | 001-project-infrastructure-setup | Project Infrastructure Setup | completed | 2026-03-12 |\n   6→| F-002 | 002-telegram-pipeline-command-router | Telegram Pipeline Command Router | completed | 2026-03-12 |\n   7→| F-003 | 003-feature-and-bug-plan-ingestion | Feature and Bug Plan Ingestion | completed | 2026-03-12 |\n   8→| F-004 | 004-pipeline-process-controller | Pipeline Process Controller | completed | 2026-03-12 |\n   9→| F-005 | 005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming | Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming | completed | 2026-03-13 |\n  10→\n  11→## F-001: Project Infrastructure Setup\n  12→\n  13→**Status:** completed  \n  14→**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n  15→\n  16→### Deliverables\n  17→\n  18→- `src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js` - Unified config loading with ENV/CLI override\n  19→- `src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js` - Feature/bug/session path resolution\n  20→- `src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js` - Error code definitions and factories\n  21→- `src/pipeline-infra/script-runner.js` - Script execution wrapper\n  22→- `src/pipeline-infra/index.js` - Module entry point\n  23→- `src/services/pipeline-control-service.js` - High-level pipeline control API\n  24→- `dev-pipeline/scripts/path_policy.py` - Python path policy mirror\n  25→- Unit tests in `tests/pipeline-infra/` and `tests/services/`\n  26→- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f001-user-stories.integration.test.js`\n  27→- Documentation in `.prizm-docs/runtime/pipeline-infra.prizm` and `.prizm-docs/pipeline/scripts.prizm`\n  28→\n  29→### Acceptance Criteria Met\n  30→\n  31→- US-1: Unified config loading