{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312045345ca952d4786694ca6","session_id":"531490f3-af15-4b63-b1c5-2c677e54409f","message":{"id":"20260312045345ca952d4786694ca6","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_3e452605e2e244e1a5105407","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/REGISTRY.md","new_string":"- NFR-1: Status aggregation < 200ms, log read < 300ms\n- NFR-2: Push failures don't block pipeline (queue + retry)\n- NFR-3: Test coverage > 85%\n\n---\n\n## F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n\n**Status:** completed\n**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n\n### Deliverables\n\n- `src/security/permission-guard.js` - Three-tier permission model (admin/operator/viewer) with env config\n- `src/security/param-sanitizer.js` - Parameter sanitization with path traversal and shell injection protection\n- `src/security/confirmation-manager.js` - Text-based confirmation flow with 60s timeout\n- `src/security/guard.js` - Unified guard middleware for command handlers\n- `src/security/system-guard.js` - System exec command guard with ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC control\n- `src/security/index.js` - Module exports\n- `src/services/audit-log-service.js` - JSON Lines audit logging with rotation (10MB/5 files)\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/audit.js` - /audit command for log query (admin-only)\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js` - Updated with force-unlock, confirmation flow, audit logging\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - Updated with confirmation flow\n- `src/config.js` - Extended with security configuration\n- `.env.example` - Updated with USER_PERMISSIONS, AUDIT_LOG_* vars\n- Unit tests in `tests/security/`\n- Unit tests in `tests/services/audit-log-service.test.js`\n- Integration tests in `tests/integration/security-flow.test.js`, `tests/integration/security-extended.test.js`\n- Documentation in `.prizm-docs/runtime/security.prizm`\n\n### Acceptance Criteria Met\n\n- US-1: User Permission Levels - Three-tier model (admin/operator/viewer) with USER_PERMISSIONS env config\n- US-2: High-Risk Command Authorization - stop/reset/force-unlock require admin, retry requires operator\n- US-3: Parameter Sanitization - Path traversal, shell injection, and dangerous character protection\n- US-4: Confirmation for Sensitive Actions - Text-based CONFIRM with 60s timeout, --force for admin\n- US-5: Audit Logging - JSON Lines format with rotation, query by user/time/action\n\n### High-Risk Command Matrix\n\n| Command | Min Permission | Confirmation |\n|---------|---------------|--------------|\n| `stop` | admin | Yes (--force skips) |\n| `reset` | admin | Yes (--force skips) |\n| `retry` | operator | No |\n| `exec` | admin | No (ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC) |\n| `force-unlock` | admin | Yes (--force skips) |\n\n### Key Decisions\n\n- D1: Three-tier permission model (admin/operator/viewer)\n- D2: Text-based confirmation (\"CONFIRM\") instead of inline keyboard\n- D3: JSON Lines audit log format with rotation\n- D4: --force flag only for admin users\n\n### Verification\n\n- Code review: PASS_WITH_WARNINGS\n- All 22 tasks completed\n- Unit tests: 90+ passing\n- Integration tests: 43+ passing","old_string":"- NFR-1: Status aggregation < 200ms, log read < 300ms\n- NFR-2: Push failures don't block pipeline (queue + retry)\n- NFR-3: Test coverage > 85%"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":53079,"output_tokens":796,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:54:07.068Z","_requestId":"1836a01aa07b4323b33253678e844458"}
